course_title: PROMOTING HEALTH AND WELLNESS FOR POPULATIONS
description: Explores population-based intervention for occupational justice, health and wellness. Provides a basic set of competencies in the domains central to the field of public health including systems thinking, social determinants of health, and health care reform policy.
